_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6395,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/15\/wife-consent-nikah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33263,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Marriage: Wife must consent to her Nikah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, should women be asked for their consent before marriage?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYes.\u201d I said, \u201cA virgin might be shy to speak when asked.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cHer silence is her consent.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6946,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12976,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/19\/nikah-obedience-allah-marriage\/","url_meta":{"origin":33263,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Nikah: Obedience to Allah is best for marriage","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 19, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Fatimah bint Qays reported: Her husband divorced her three times, and the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon her, had not appointed her housing or maintenance. The Prophet said to her, \u201cWhen your waiting period is over, come to me.\u201d Fatimah came to him as she was given\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6392,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/15\/nikah-marriage-without-consent\/","url_meta":{"origin":33263,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Nikah: If a woman married without consent","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Khansa' bint Khidam reported: Her father married her off after her previous marriage ended, but she disliked it. She came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he annulled their marriage. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5138 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari Imam Ibn Hajar commented,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15508,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/29\/go-to-hajj-with-wife\/","url_meta":{"origin":33263,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Go perform pilgrimage with your wife","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA man should not be alone with a woman, nor should a woman travel unless a guardian is with her.\u201d A man stood up and said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I have been assigned to a military expedition,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35722,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuam